      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;ancestral-unique-quarterstaff-rod-of-kepeleke&#34;&gt;[Ancestral Unique QuarterStaff] Rod of Kepeleke&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;800 Item Power&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;596 Damage Per Second&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;[434 - 650] Damage per Hit&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;1.10 Attacks per Second (Fast)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;45% Block Chance&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;+[12 - 24] Maximum Resource&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;+[80.0 - 100.0]% Critical Damage&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+52.5% Chance for Core Skills to Hit Twice&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;+[2 - 4] to Velocity (Spiritborn Only)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Requires Level: 60&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div markdown=&#34;span&#34; class=&#34;bs-callout-v2 bs-callout-v2-warning bs-callout-v2-level-1&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;Your Core Skills are now additionally Basic Skills and free to cast, but deal up to 30% reduced damage based on their Vigor Cost.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
